descriptionHtml:
Quantfury is a global brokerage that offers commission-free trading and investing at real-time spot prices of global and crypto exchanges.

Buy or sell 500 assets including: USA and European stocks, crypto pairs, commodity and stock index futures, ETFs and forex pairs. There are no trade commissions, fees for using leverage, or any other type of fees.

BUY OR SELL AT GLOBAL AND CRYPTO EXCHANGE PRICES
Buy and sell price quotes are delivered in real-time from exchanges, such as NYSE, NASDAQ, BATS Europe, LSE, CME, NYMEX, and Binance.

INVEST & RECEIVE DIVIDENDS
Receive full stock and ETF dividends in their nominal value converted into the cryptocurrency of your account balance.

GET FREE STOCK OR FREE CRYPTO
Join Quantfury, invite friends, and you’ll both get a free stock like AAPL or UBER, or free crypto like BTC or ETH when they join.

24/7 IN-APP SUPPORT
Quantfury industry-leading, blazing fast support team is available in the app 24/7 to assist Quantfurians.
